des: Understanding your annual enrollment and benefit questions can be difficult if you don’t use the correct terminologies. UTC Healthy You helps provide UTC employees with answers to annual enrollment and benefit questions when you use your own words. This skill helps UTC employees stay informed about the latest UTC benefit information and choices available.
